text = "khaal can transform/control monsters
previous territory of the Manok and Varoma that was taken over when K'haal was banished, now ruled by him and his henchmen, a wasteland even more dead than the Unim desert.
kaluta have the goal of bringing khaal to the mortal plane
Red Robe, the previous Councillor of Affairs before Jhon (cool stuff here, killed by Tonitrus Thunderblood)
before kaluta the land was half varoman and half manokan
the Blood Invasions are attacks by the Kalutans during their early years in attempt to capture pieces of Volin, they failed mostly between 2916PD-2923PD"
